::Cygnar::
    "Well...  We've got a good dozen.  Probably more if we need them.  And I 
am having us sneak in from behind them to pin them down, cut off all escape.  
Once they're out of the fight they are to be captured.  First we must take 
the base and reconfigure it to accept Destrons.  I should've realized this 
sooner."  He opens a com to Guiledart and NeoGuile.  "Can either of you come 
to the Syria base I have a job for you."
